# FootballAPI

FootballAPI is a simple API allowing consumers query information on football matches and players.
This first version will focus on the matches of FCPorto.

## Teams Collection [/v1/teams]

### Get all Teams [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "teams":[
                {
                    "name": "Futebol Clube do Porto",
                    "shortName": "FCP",
                    "website": "http://www.fcp.pt",
                    "email": "info@",
                    "founded": 1896,
                    "clubColors": "Azul e Branco",
                    "venue": "Estadio do Dragao",
                    "id":1
                },
                {
                    "name": "Liverpool",
